title: [Brisker's Cove, Comyner Court]
description: Cracked white tiles form a radiated, wavy-rayed sun around a circular sandstone fountain that dominates the quiet courtyard.  Torches illuminate the faces of many a shop and home that surround the small gathering place, and though many are closed for the evening a stucco and oak store remains open to customers.
paths: Obvious paths: northeast, southeast, southwest, northwest
